{"type":"data","nodes":[null,{"type":"data","data":[{"studio":1},{"description":2,"blocks":3,"seo":23,"_seoMetaTags":29},"ZIID® is a creative studio using artificial intelligence to expand human creativity. The eye represents our most essential tool in a world overwhelmed with visual stimuli. We collaborate across diverse industries and cultural landscapes reflecting our belief that variety drives our creative process. Each project at ZIID® is backed by thorough research, ensuring that our creative decisions are deliberate and meaningful. No project is too small for us, we see each one as an opportunity to express ourselves. We love what we do. ",[4,10,15,19],{"label":5,"lines":6},"Clients",[7],{"id":8,"text":9},"coming-soon-clients","Coming soon!",{"label":11,"lines":12},"Services",[13],{"id":14,"text":9},"coming-soon-services",{"label":16,"lines":17},"Press",[18],{"text":9},{"label":20,"lines":21},"Recognitions",[22],{"text":9},{"image":24,"title":27,"description":28},{"alt":25,"url":26},null,"/www.datocms-assets.com/127841/1763650338-unveil_seo_2.png","Studio","ZIID® is a creative studio using artificial intelligence to expand human creativity.",[30,34,38,41,44,47,50,54,58,62,65,69,73,77,81,85,89],{"__typename":31,"attributes":25,"content":32,"tag":33},"Tag","Studio — ZIID®","title",{"__typename":31,"attributes":35,"content":25,"tag":37},{"property":36,"content":27},"og:title","meta",{"__typename":31,"attributes":39,"content":25,"tag":37},{"name":40,"content":27},"twitter:title",{"__typename":31,"attributes":42,"content":25,"tag":37},{"name":43,"content":28},"description",{"__typename":31,"attributes":45,"content":25,"tag":37},{"property":46,"content":28},"og:description",{"__typename":31,"attributes":48,"content":25,"tag":37},{"name":49,"content":28},"twitter:description",{"__typename":31,"attributes":51,"content":25,"tag":37},{"property":52,"content":53},"og:image","/www.datocms-assets.com/127841/1763650338-unveil_seo_2.png?auto=format&fit=max&w=1200",{"__typen